{"tid":547926,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大通過改國歌歌詞　杜魯多：性別平等邁進一步","createTime":"2018-02-02T03:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T01:56:07.000Z","uid":48083,"like":17,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"0f64f1526e11533e74aadf3a4c1e1e1137d9a19c","tid":547926,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T03:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/justin-04_1xdA1_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fjustin-04_1xdA1_1200x0.png&h=ad447dbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多年來，加拿大國歌《O Canada》其中一句歌詞－－「愛國真心，統領您眾兒子」，被指涉嫌性別不平等。去年，有議員提案要求修定，參議院最終於當地時間本周三通過修定國歌歌詞法案。<br />\n<br />\n早在 2013 年，加拿大作家 Margaret Atwood 與前總理 Kim Campbell 等知名女性，推動修定國歌《啊，加拿大》（O Canada）的運動，期望歌詞更能呈現性別中立。她們建議把歌詞「True patriot love, in all thy sons command.」（愛國真心，統領您眾兒子），修定為「True patriot love, in all of us command」（愛國真心，統領我們）。<br />\n<br />\n2016 年，加拿大眾議員 Mauril B&eacute;langer 將討論帶入議會，並於眾議院獲得大比數支持。議案獲安大略獨立參選員 Frances Lankin 帶到參議院，經過 18 個月來的討論，本周三順利完成三讀獲得通過。Frances Lankin 事後形容，改動雖小，只是兩個字的差異，但意義具大，「之後再唱國歌會更感驕傲」。加拿大總理杜魯多昨日亦於 Twitter 發訊恭賀，形容法案是「邁向性別平等的另一步」。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\nJustin Trudeau<br />\n✔<br />\n@JustinTrudeau<br />\nMauril&rsquo;s bill to make O Canada gender neutral passed third reading in the Senate tonight - another positive step towards gender equality. #inallofuscommand<br />\n<br />\n上午8:52 - 2018年2月1日<br />\n 1,266 1,266 則回覆   1,149 1,149 個轉推   4,874 4,874 個喜歡<br />\nTwitter 廣告資訊與隱私<br />\n雖然如此，部分保守派參議員感到失望，其中保守黨參議院領袖 Larry Smith 更形容法案獲得通過是「不幸」，一眾保守黨參議員亦拒絕參與同日晚上的投票，以示不滿。<br />\n<br />\n《O Canada》寫成於 1903 年，原為教會的愛國音樂，1939 年起成為加拿大國歌，但其官方地位一直要到 1980 年才獲確認。數十年來，不少加國人提出歌詞未能呈現性別中立，過去曾 12 度提出修改國歌的議案亦未獲通過。修定法案日前最終獲得確認，惟去年將討論帶入議會的眾議員 Mauril B&eacute;langer 病逝，未能親身見證成果。<br />\n<br />\n相關報道：<br />\n<br />\nIndependent／Guardian／CBC／The Canadian Press<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E4%BF%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E6%AD%8C%E8%A9%9E-%E6%9D%9C%E9%AD%AF%E5%A4%9A-%E6%80%A7%E5%88%A5%E5%B9%B3%E7%AD%89%E9%82%81%E9%80%B2%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%258B%25BF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AD%258C%25E6%25AD%258C%25E8%25A9%259E-%25E6%259D%259C%25E9%25AD%25AF%25E5%25A4%259A-%25E6%2580%25A7%25E5%2588%25A5%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E7%25AD%2589%25E9%2582%2581%25E9%2580%25B2%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25AD%25A5%2F&d=t38vdQYCPkB44LpmfOizJZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=3b9817b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%258B%25BF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AD%258C%25E6%25AD%258C%25E8%25A9%259E-%25E6%259D%259C%25E9%25AD%25AF%25E5%25A4%259A-%25E6%2580%25A7%25E5%2588%25A5%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E7%25AD%2589%25E9%2582%2581%25E9%2580%25B2%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25AD%25A5%2F&h=3a126ed9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E4%BF%AE%E5%AE%9A%E5%9C%8B%E6%AD%8C%E6%AD%8C%E8%A9%9E-%E6%9D%9C%E9%AD%AF%E5%A4%9A-%E6%80%A7%E5%88%A5%E5%B9%B3%E7%AD%89%E9%82%81%E9%80%B2%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5/</a>"},{"pid":"80a1ad68363efdbd24af9a4a31882bb74f4e4caa","tid":547926,"uid":92178,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T04:01:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"238cca646bad1edea04e55cd1bff648067b39352","tid":547926,"uid":132859,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T04:18:51.000Z","msg":"liberal準備好收皮未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecec17060d1e9501b26df7267bac556ff8995257","tid":547926,"uid":38425,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T04:21:47.000Z","msg":"我駛唔駛un下un下咁唱"},{"pid":"b05324905f75409701b4f716f6f